{"tid":2035473,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「唔好屌住」527唔好去港島去其他地方好唔好？","createTime":"2020-05-26T02:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T05:26:12.000Z","uid":197235,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"176909c32ce5bb79b7dbcd72dd8f822b594fb55c","tid":2035473,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:46:04.000Z","msg":"立法會已經<span style=\"color: red;\">唔屬於香港人</span><br />\n<br />\n2019年送中條例係中共港共仲有顧忌先終止<br />\n<br />\n2020連國安法都出埋 你覺得佢地仲會理香港人？<br />\n<br />\n你527當日可以阻止 第二日 第三日 都無可能持續落去<br />\n<br />\n再講獻世派<span style=\"color: red;\">要立法可以去其他地方做</span><br />\n<br />\n佢地選主席已經<span style=\"color: red;\">「搲」爛塊面唔使再做戲</span><br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得我叫人唔好出黎<br />\n<br />\n咁<span style=\"color: red;\">你就錯</span><br />\n<br />\n我只係<span style=\"color: red;\">叫你唔好去難走難打易被捕嘅港島</span><br />\n<br />\n而係九龍 <br />\n<br />\n可能你覺得九龍同港島一樣<br />\n<br />\n但我會覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">九龍容易集人 容易走人</span><br />\n<br />\n尖咀到美孚/樂富任你走<br />\n<br />\n只要<span style=\"color: red;\">不陣地戰 互相幫助 睇住手足</span>一定比港島好<br />\n<br />\n可能你話<span style=\"color: red;\">九龍阻止唔到立法會</span><br />\n<br />\n但係實際上<span style=\"color: red;\">你港島金鐘都入唔到 </span><br />\n<br />\n依加最重要係向國際展示<span style=\"color: red;\">反抗意志</span><br />\n<br />\n只要我地有<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭行為 </span><span style=\"color: red;\">不需介懷地方</span> 國際會知道 <br />\n<br />\n根本唔需要<span style=\"color: red;\">送羊入虎口</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">保存生命 才能長期抗爭</span><br />\n<br />\n最後祝港人有<span style=\"color: red;\">自由意志 </span>清楚真正目標<br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\">中共攬炒，港人迎戰</span>」"},{"pid":"62aff9529b25bddeef32e01835a52d7d4305b2fc","tid":2035473,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:46:21.000Z","msg":"開花？"},{"pid":"656c3e2867e5dbb721a16bb2843683bcc6dc0072","tid":2035473,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:46:33.000Z","msg":"九龍？"},{"pid":"0a330633bd9d5343ad0f8863db78e26d285e659a","tid":2035473,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"獻世屋企？"},{"pid":"6e9d85ac7705bd64ac77700382ca4d93557b297d","tid":2035473,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"獻世屋企？"},{"pid":"65511d6430f10bfb772df2efb11e3ac39965cb73","tid":2035473,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:46:54.000Z","msg":"獻世屋企？"},{"pid":"e34234584318bbbc884368c4d30d0824a5f9456b","tid":2035473,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:46:57.000Z","msg":"獻世屋企？"},{"pid":"79030d2a7a8c4de992621f5a613b385bdb733f06","tid":2035473,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:47:32.000Z","msg":"港島要三思"},{"pid":"746a2ea5f162dfc5c1b67946b68fcaf237a7bb33","tid":2035473,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T02:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9e2dca60580f94371974304f8b76b792a2c524","tid":2035473,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,